name: Astro Globes: Orion's Belt
description:
Astro Globes is a series of uniquely processed astrophotography from my own collection with each image featuring a different object in our skies.
The asterism of Orion's belt features prominently in this widefield photo of the constellation Orion, with the Orion nebular and the stars Betelgeuse and Rigel visible on the outer edges.
